{"tid":1013870,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[HR] 新年新工 有問必答","createTime":"2019-02-08T16:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T10:53:44.000Z","uid":143184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4ba63d28e55832bdb0603c43cd4cc8a83a22eff2","tid":1013870,"uid":143184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T16:25:35.000Z","msg":"工作經驗:一年又6 month. (工程)<br />\n其實依家都唔想係呢個部門做 無前途可言.原本想做夠2年 就過檔,依家想讀番書top up degree full time <br />\n1.又驚唔收(gpa=2.3)   <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.唔想留係呢部門 一定會quite <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3. 如現公司hr肯留我同調部門  可唔quit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我想3情況發生 .呢方面仲會冇得報U.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但同時唔俾調部門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唯有焗走新公司    但1報左u   3又唔使諗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> . <br />\n好煩惱啊方丈大人點睇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ....報u又可以轉文職 唔使做到死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 另一方面同時調部門 又學X多左野   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef21f966933b85f6c70df7cab81934e82025eec2","tid":1013870,"uid":143184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T16:26:47.000Z","msg":"點del post  錯手禁左"},{"pid":"d2b5e9560f813767ebc39e432d138fc6ee78d273","tid":1013870,"uid":115910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef21f966933b85f6c70df7cab81934e82025eec2","tid":1013870,"uid":143184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T16:26:47.000Z","msg":"點del post  錯手禁左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T16:27:57.000Z","msg":"去站務台同管理員講"},{"pid":"729cd81742d3468e05637fd81727b10cee95ad1d","tid":1013870,"uid":146376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0